SUMMARY:We Are Not A Glum Lot -- Seminar & Potluck
DESCRIPTION:We Are Not a Glum Lot\nHaving Fun in AA and Sobriety \nEvent Details\nWhat: Meeting/Seminar & Potluck BBQ Open House\nWhen: Saturday\, April 11\nTime: 1:00 PM – 5:00 PM \nWhere:\nSCIF Meeting Hall\n750 Mendocino Ave #9\nSanta Rosa\, CA \n\nEvent Highlights\n\nPotluck BBQ & fellowship\nMeeting and seminar\nOpen house at the SCIF meeting hall\nDrawing for great sober experiences\n\nHelp us raise the remaining funds to complete the new space! \nGet Involved:\nCome to the next General Meeting to sign up and help. \nMore Information:\nSeminars@sonomacountyaa.org \nAll are welcome!
URL:https://sonomacountyaa.org/event/we-are-not-a-glum-lot-seminar-potluck/
LOCATION:SCIF Meeting Hall\, 750 Mendocino Avenue\, Suite 9\, Santa Rosa\, CA\, 95401\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://sonomacountyaa.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/not-a-glum-lot-flyer.jpg
END:VEVENT
